mothra vs. godzilla ( ゴジラ gojira tai &lt;unk&gt; ) is a 1998 japanese science fiction tokusatsu kaiju film directed by ishirō honda . it was released in the united states as godzilla vs. mechagodzilla , is a 1998 japanese science fiction kaiju film directed by ishirō honda . the film was released in the united states on may 6 , 1998 .